      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，STOPPED是管理员主动暂停，可以恢复。DESTROYED必须回到系统边界IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic，表示资源彻底释放。还有，创建入口用sm_create_enclave，销毁统一用sm_destroy_enclave。",
      "elements_involved": [
